{"root":{"data":{"id":"dif904ui4qo0","created":1778441801761,"text":"Game Rift","note":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dig4l91jusg0","created":1778530910949,"text":"Transition","expandState":"expand","background":"#00b0f0","layout":null,"note":"提交翻译需求:\n  1. 在思维导图提交翻译需求\n  2. 填写:\n    * 视频名\n    * 完成度\n    * 超连接\n    * 简介\n\n下载资源:\n  1. Gihosoft TubeGet下载\n    * video.mp4\n    * cover.jpg\n  2. BiliDown\n \n\n视频制作流程:\n  1. Videolingo->归档[配音完成]\n  2. 归档移至[配音完成] -> [素材]\n  3. MSST分离原视频的BGM -> [素材]\n    1. 提取视频伴奏BGM\n    2. 将dub.mp3和BGM降噪为dry\n  4. 将封面Cover.jpg移至[视频名]\n  5. Kdenlive:\n    * 导入\n      dub.srt\n      BGM.wav\n      original_video\n      normalized_dub.wav\n      dub.srt\n    * 观看并校对字幕\n    * 导出视频->[视频名]\n    * 导出字幕->[视频名]\n  6. 删除无关文件, 保留如下结构\n  文件夹结构:\n  * [配音完成]\n    * [视频名]\n      * [素材]\n        * dub.srt\n        * original_video.mp4\n        * normalized_dub.wav\n        * BGM.wav -> MSST\n    *  Cover.jpg\n    *  最终视频.mp4\n    *  最终字幕.srt\n    \n发布:\n  * 上传视频\n  * 提交字幕\n  \n  \n    "},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dif9859df2w0","created":1778442429573,"text":"Course","expandState":"expand","layout":null,"background":"#4e6128"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dif8a0qs2hk0","created":1778439755360,"text":"Godot","layout":null,"background":"#76923c","color":"white"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dif8abewpnk0","created":1778439778587,"text":"How to Create a 3D Survival Game in Godot 4.2 with GDScript","progress":1,"layout":null,"background":"transparent"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"digztej9ws00","created":1778619004225,"text":"[gdquest]终极 Godot 捆绑包 | Ultimate Godot Bundle","priority":"1"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dif8acqd6rc0","created":1778439781457,"text":"Blender","layout":null,"expandState":"expand","background":"#76923c","color":"white"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dif8ayc3khc0","created":1778439828483,"text":"Blender  Ultimate Game Art Creation Guide","progress":1,"layout":null,"background":"transparent"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dif8ilthgj40","created":1778440428150,"text":"Blender  Ultimate Game Art Creation Guide","progress":1,"layout":null,"background":"transparent"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dif8wvcfihs0","created":1778441545985,"text":"Alive! Animation course in Blender","progress":1,"layout":null,"background":"transparent"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"digzonb0yaw0","created":1778618631496,"text":"[gamedev tv] Blender 纹理绘画：创建风格化模型 | Blender Texture Painting: Create Stylised Models","progress":1},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"digzv4iiku80","created":1778619139139,"text":"[Udemy]终极 Blender 3D 雕刻课程 | The Ultimate Blender 3D Sculpting Course","progress":1},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dif8agzw6sg0","created":1778439790740,"text":"Sounds","layout":null,"background":"#76923c","color":"white"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dif8c0d7kbc0","created":1778439911268,"text":"Game Audio Essentials Music Production for Video Games","layout":null,"progress":1,"background":"transparent"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dif8c6i3c800","created":1778439924624,"text":"Game Audio Essentials SFX & Sound Design For Video Games","progress":1,"layout":null,"background":"transparent"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"digzk2534qw0","created":1778618271968,"text":"Others","background":"#76923c","color":"white"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"digzkd4wkps0","created":1778618295902,"text":"[Udemy]如何成为游戏开发中的技术美术 | How to become Technical Artist in Game Development"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"digzlux2rsg0","created":1778618412975,"text":"[SimonDev]游戏数学简单解释 | Game Math Explained Simply"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"digznygicpk0","created":1778618577408,"text":"[Udemy]使用 Godot 创建您的 3D MOBA 移动游戏 | Create Your 3D MOBA Game for Mobile Using Godot"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dihu6mvxep40","created":1778704674435,"text":"Level Design Fundamentals Get Good At Making Game Levels","progress":1},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dif99h5pa280","created":1778442533837,"text":"GameDev","background":"#4e6128","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dif9bhshy1s0","created":1778442691944,"text":"Youtube","background":"#76923c","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"digu33aiek80","created":1778602836732,"text":"Godot technology","background":"#73a1bf","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"difw3jd3tmo0","created":1778506953981,"text":"用 Godot 制作的神级 3D 角色控制器，这将是我们的 ALS！","expandState":"expand","hyperlink":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qIf5YQ8qJng&t=52s","hyperlinkTitle":"atnda","note":"God Tier 3D Character Controller Made In Godot, this will be our ALS!\n\n哟！\n\n这是 Arena 项目开发日志系列的第一集。在这一集中，我将回顾控制器核心的更新，以及它与公开控制器项目的区别。核心理念当然是躯干分割。老观众应该知道，我已经在公开项目中尝试过，并且取得了一定的成功，但还称不上“神级”。然而，从那时起，情况发生了一些变化。首先，Godot 在 3D 动画方面开始有所改进，并为我们带来了 SkeletonModifier3D 技术。有了它，我就可以构建一个足够灵活的动画框架，实现完美的躯干分割和八向运动混合，而无需像以前那样依赖 AnimationTree。其次，我找到了一位专业的动画师，他可以提供高质量的八向运动包。最后，这个项目有希望有一天能够商业化，所以现在既有雄心壮志，也有资金投入，我真是忐忑不安。\n\n我对成果相当满意，这对我来说是一个非常令人安心的里程碑。当然，我目前只有几个例子可以展示它的强大之处，但我用纸笔搭建了一个框架，并逐渐意识到我可以用这些“积木”设计出整个《泰坦陨落》。这让我终于感到心安，我完成了控制器，现在可以做一些其他的事情，比如敌人、网络，甚至更好的动画工具。\n\n再次强调，目前还没有项目，但我认为这仍然是一份很好的学习资料。视频中有几段模糊的代码，它们并非“私有”，而是为了稍后几分钟的讲解而暂时隐藏起来的。最后，我还提供了一些关于如何将公共控制器重构为这个系统的建议。\n\n另外，我之前的一些视频或许对您有用：\n\n这基本上就是我用来制作动画的技术，只有一些细微的改动。\n\n• 过渡到 Godot 更强大的 3D 动画……\n\n这两个视频是我之前尝试制作躯干分裂动画的成果，它们很有价值，但请注意，现在看来它们有点过时了，要知道这是在骨骼修改器出现之前：\n\n• Godot 大型动画的分层流程……\n\n• 翻滚闪避、盾牌格挡和有限法术……\n\n如果您是新观众，不知道该怎么做，可以看看这个，我有一个 1.25 小时的教程系列，相信您会受益匪浅：\n\n• 在您的 Godot 动画中使用专业的 AAA 级制作方法……\n\n加入我们的 Discord 服务器，偶尔会有大神出现，随机帮您把主帧执行时间缩短一半！\n\n/ discord\n\n您也可以在 Patreon 上支持本频道 ^_^:\n\n/ fairfight\n\n另外，提供动画的那位大神还制作了一些超棒的 3D 工具，快去看看吧！\n\nhttps://linktr.ee/notthatnda\n\n00:00 为什么你想砍掉自己的腿\n\n02:45 Base(d) 系统\n\n10:53 简短的类回顾\n\n12:42 最终飞跃成神\n\n14:40 如何将公共项目重构为这种形式","background":"transparent","progress":1,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"difyce3go280","created":1778513290011,"text":"Godot 4 自定义检查器插件","hyperlink":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xa6YBcrrS7E&t=19s","hyperlinkTitle":"","note":"Custom Inspector Plugins Godot 4\n\n学习如何使用检查器插件完全自定义 Godot 检查器。\n\n利用检查器插件释放 Godot 编辑器的强大功能，彻底改变您的游戏制作工作流程。\n\n自定义特殊类检查器，改善您的体验，改变其信息显示方式和交互方式。\n\n································································································\n\n想支持我吗？\n\n🌐 Patreon：/octodemy\n\n🌐项目源文件：/156854028\n\n·················································································\n\n#godot4 #godot #godotengine\n\n#godot4.6 #godotinspector #godoteditor #godot3d\n\n章节：\n\n0:00 简介\n\n0:15 检查器插件\n\n3:40 EditorProperty 类\n\n7:22 警告\n\n7:43 示例 1：生命条和属性更改监听器\n\n9:17 示例 2：3D 场景","progress":1,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"digstd1d28w0","created":1778599253196,"text":"如何在真实服装上实现布料物理效果 ✨ Godot Softbody3D","hyperlink":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7higlB3ueDk&t=25s","hyperlinkTitle":"","note":"我看到很多教程教你如何用 Godot 的 Softbody 节点制作简单的四边形披风，但我一直找不到如何为绑定/蒙皮到动画网格（例如角色服装）上的服装部件制作动画的方法。所以我自己做了一个！\n\n🦑 我在哪里？\n\n网站：https://www.savallion.com\n\n贴纸商店：https://savallionart.etsy.com\n\nTwitch 直播：/savallion\n\nInstagram：/thesavallion\n\nMedium：/lysscreative\n\n☕ https://ko-fi.com/savallion\n\n如果你喜欢这个视频，可以通过观看更多我的视频、在 Twitch 上和我互动，或者点击上面的链接请我喝杯咖啡来支持我！","progress":9},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"digu1bssto00","created":1778602698524,"text":"Godot 4.0 中的动态布娃娃/物理动画","hyperlink":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0MHY2TDeMLM","hyperlinkTitle":"","note":"本周我一直在尝试以虚幻引擎的物理动画风格实现动态布娃娃系统。希望你们喜欢最终效果！\n\nGitHub：\n\nhttps://github.com/CBerry22/Active-Ragdoll---Physics-Animations-in-Godot-4.0\n\n资源：\n\nhttps://docs.godotengine.org/en/stable/classes/class_skeleton3d.html\n\nhttps://docs.godotengine.org/en/stable/classes/class_physicalbone3d.html\n\n社交媒体：\n\nTwitch - / crigz\n\nTwitter - / pixelpunkgames1","progress":1},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dim1z5mwu4g0","created":1779132897042,"text":"GDC","background":"#73a1bf"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"classic","version":"1.4.43"}